 Brentwood, Franklin, and the rest of the Middle Tennessee area. Tankless and tank water heaters, sewer and drain, water filtration, kitchen and bath plumbing, and full repipes are our day-to-day work. Service you can trust."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-ink","children":"— Aaron Kelly"}]]}]]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-forest text-bone-50 py-16 lg:py-24","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"eyebrow text-copper-light mb-3","children":"How we work"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display text-3xl lg:text-4xl mb-12 leading-tight max-w-2xl","children":["Four promises on"," ",["$","span",null,{"className":"italic","children":"every single job."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8","children":[["$","div","Flat-price quotes, no surprises",{"className":"border-l-2 border-copper pl-6 py-2","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-display text-xs tracking-[0.2em] text-copper-light","children":"01"}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl mt-2 mb-3","children":"Flat-price quotes, no surprises"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-bone-100/80 leading-relaxed","children":"Every job is quoted as a flat price after diagnosis — parts, labor, and any required permits all itemized. No per-hour open meter, no mid-job upcharges, no 'we found something extra' once we've started. The number we tell you up front is the number you pay."}]]}],["$","div","Licensed master plumber on every job",{"className":"border-l-2 border-copper pl-6 py-2","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-display text-xs tracking-[0.2em] text-copper-light","children":"02"}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl mt-2 mb-3","children":"Licensed master plumber on every job"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-bone-100/80 leading-relaxed","children":"Aaron Kelly is the licensed Tennessee Master Plumber on record — license #4034, verifiable on the 